data.description: MOTIVATED AND NEWLY PAINTED COME TAKE A LOOK - Living, Dining, Kitchen, Primary Bedroom & Bath, Hallway!!! Just down the street from White Wing Golf Course, you will find this thoughtfully modified & updated DeVaca home on a beautiful "treed" lot with no grass to cut! While the trees offer privacy, the interior offers plenty of living & storage space. Enter through a custom cut glass front door. On your right, what was once a bedroom is now a flex room with French doors - you choose its use - sunroom, den/study, bedroom. The great room & kitchen are perfectly situated for the open floor plan this model offers. The kitchen has a generous breakfast area, granite island & counters, lots of cabinets (lower with roll-outs), filtered sink water & mostly GE appliances. The large great room, combo formal dining & living, has custom built-ins, a custom tiled gas log fireplace with mantel, and opens to a large, enclosed back porch with screened-in extension. With window & screens, solar ceiling panels, stand-alone cooling & heating, fire pit & gas connection, there is plenty of room for entertaining or enjoying the outdoors without being outdoors! The primary bath has a jacuzzi, walk-in shower & double vanity; the guest bath, a walk-in shower. The utility room doubles as an office & laundry with built-in desk & cabinets. The extended garage has built-in storage, wire shelving, mud sink, finished floors, 50-gal hot water heater (2021), water softener & central vac. Throughout the home, there are custom light fixtures, ceiling fans, solar tubes & crown molding. Roof shingles were replaced in 2021. Laminate wood flooring & carpet installed in 2021.
